					<h1>A Vanilla JS Micro-Library</h1>

					<p class="space-bottom-small">Buoy is a simple micro-library that makes working with vanilla JS a little bit easier.</p>

					<ul>
					    <li>Add, remove, toggle and check for classes.</li>
					    <li>Get an object's sibling elements.</li>
					</ul>

					<hr>

				</div>
			</div>

		</article>
